<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Ruskin Bond writes stories for children. He wants children to learn the value of relationships. He wants to convey this message to all that - 'Relatio<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Ruskin Bond writes stories for children. He wants children to learn the value of relationships. He wants to convey this message to all that - 'Relationships are more important than possessions.'<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
