    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_4350335326" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4350335326" />
    <a title="Jane" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/92480025-jane"><img alt="Jane" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1637432159p2/92480025.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4350335326?book_show_action=true">Nov 22, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jane" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jane" href="/user/show/92480025-jane">Jane</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/92480025-jane?shelf=2021">2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/92480025-jane?shelf=childrens">childrens</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/92480025-jane?shelf=5-star-amazing">5-star-amazing</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/92480025-jane?shelf=inspiring">inspiring</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/92480025-jane?shelf=physical-books-i-own">physical-books-i-own</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4350335326" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7390755802221852432">When Binya first laid eyes on the blue umbrella, she fell in love with it. It&apos;s the prettiest thing she had ever seen! Since one of the picnickers wants her leopard claw necklace, Binya got a chance to exchange it with the blue umbrella. Finally, she have it as her own.<br/><br/>Binya use it everyday wherever she goes and she always open it since she finds it prettier than when it&apos;s close. The blue umbrella is the prettiest thing in their village. Everybody looks at her whenever she pass by using her umbr</span>
  <span id="freeText7390755802221852432" style="display:none">When Binya first laid eyes on the blue umbrella, she fell in love with it. It's the prettiest thing she had ever seen! Since one of the picnickers wants her leopard claw necklace, Binya got a chance to exchange it with the blue umbrella. Finally, she have it as her own.<br /><br />Binya use it everyday wherever she goes and she always open it since she finds it prettier than when it's close. The blue umbrella is the prettiest thing in their village. Everybody looks at her whenever she pass by using her umbrella. Even though the colour fade through time, Binya still love her beautiful umbrella.<br /><br />This is the first book that I have read from Ruskin Bond. It's a heartfelt story. It's about greed, envy and forgiveness. It shows that everybody can change if they are given a chance. It also shows that relationships are more important than material things in life.<br /><br />Overall, a great easy to digest read! </span>
  <a data-text-id="7390755802221852432" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


