<div id="review_3518118698" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3518118698" />
    <a title="Aswathy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/104558622-aswathy"><img alt="Aswathy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1593229900p2/104558622.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3518118698?book_show_action=true">Aug 28, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Aswathy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Aswathy" href="/user/show/104558622-aswathy">Aswathy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3518118698" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13799995253195377004">I finished reading The blue umbrella by Ruskin Bond yesterday and I must admit that I am totally in love with the book.Only after reading this book,I realized that how much I was in need of a light and simple read.<br/><br/><br/>The blue umbrella by Ruskin Bond is the story of Binya and her beautiful blue umbrella. It&apos;s a really beautiful story which will make you smile and also, happy. The language is so simple and the writing style is commendable. I totally enjoyed the storyline and I am really happy that I </span>
  <span id="freeText13799995253195377004" style="display:none">I finished reading The blue umbrella by Ruskin Bond yesterday and I must admit that I am totally in love with the book.Only after reading this book,I realized that how much I was in need of a light and simple read.<br /><br /><br />The blue umbrella by Ruskin Bond is the story of Binya and her beautiful blue umbrella. It's a really beautiful story which will make you smile and also, happy. The language is so simple and the writing style is commendable. I totally enjoyed the storyline and I am really happy that I happened to read this book. Another interesting thing about the book is that it has cute illustrations /drawings that goes with the story. <br /><br /><br />It's a perfect book for beginners who want to start with their reading habit. And also, I think it's a perfect book to bring you out of a reading slump.Tbh, I can't wait to read other books written by Ruskin Bond.<br /><br /><br />.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13799995253195377004" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


